steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Team" without submenu
Then I should see Team screen display
When I invite existing account "staging_tester2" to project
Then I should see the warning popup with message "User invitation sent successfully"
Then I should see row index "2" has Name - Email of account "staging_tester2" - status "Activated"
Debug step:
Debug step:
Debug step:
When I logout the current account
When I login to Jitera product by account "staging_tester2"
When I edit timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jit001" and Comment "Testing to add new table"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit001" display
When I navigate to menu "Modules" without submenu
Then I should see Modules screen display
When I add module "Force Mobile Update"
Then I should see module "Force Mobile Update" was added by Remove button
When I navigate to menu "API" with submenu "API endpoints"
Then I should see API screen display
Then I should see group api "force_update_app_versions" displayed in api list
When I select api name "force_update_app_versions" from list
When I wait query data API "force_update_app_versions.platform" is fetched completely
